Package com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.datastore

The package provides classes to manage the datastore and storagepod config.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Datastore
    Datastore class defines the spec for datastore configurations in vCenter Server.
    Datastore.Builder
    Builder class for Datastore.
    DatastoreFactory
    DatastoreFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.datastore package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
    MaintenanceModeState
    The MaintenanceModeState enumeration class defines the maintenance mode states of the datastore.
    PodStorageDrsEntry
    The PodStorageDrsEntry class contains spec to define storage DRS related attributes of the Storage Pod.
    PodStorageDrsEntry.Builder
    Builder class for PodStorageDrsEntry.
    StorageDrsConfigInfo
    The StorageDrsConfigInfo class contains spec to define storage DRS configurations.
    StorageDrsConfigInfo.Builder
    Builder class for StorageDrsConfigInfo.
    StorageDrsPodConfigInfo
    The StorageDrsConfigInfo class contains spec to define pod-wide configuration information for the storage DRS service.
    StorageDrsPodConfigInfo.Builder
    Builder class for StorageDrsPodConfigInfo.
    StoragePod
    The StoragePod class contains spec to define storage pod in vCenter Server.
    StoragePod.Builder
    Builder class for StoragePod.
    StructDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.appliance.vcenter.settings.v1.config.components.inventory.datastore package.
    Summary
    Summary class defines the datastore summary properties.
    Summary.Builder
    Builder class for Summary.
